data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch home! This home features a beautifully updated kitchen with modern appliances and plenty of counter space. Hardwood floors throughout the main floor gives this home a solid feel and easy to maintain style! The cozy finished basement offers additional living space and storage options. The updated finished full bath in the basement is very spacious and convenient for a family. Outside, you'll find a premium fenced yard on a spacious corner lot and a lot of privacy!
